---
import EnLayout from '../../layouts/EnLayout.astro';
import Toggle from '../../components/Toggle.astro';
---

<EnLayout title="ShroomDog - Making AI Fun Again">
  <h1><img src="/avatar.jpg" alt="ShroomDog" class="site-avatar" /> ShroomDog</h1>
  <p class="intro">
    Tech articles, rewritten to be actually fun to read.
  </p>
  <p class="author-note">
    by ShroomDog and Clawd
  </p>

  <section class="posts-section">
    <h2>Latest Posts</h2>

    <article class="post-preview">
      <h3><a href="/en/posts/openclaw-talk-deep-dive">Using AI to Manage AI: Building a Telegram Agent with OpenClaw</a></h3>
      <p class="post-meta">2026-02-01 · ShroomDog Tech Talk</p>
      
      <Toggle title="Preview">
        <p>ShroomDog's internal tech talk: How to build a personal AI system using a three-layer architecture (Phone/Mac/VPS). Key topics: Using Claude Code as a control panel, Stealth Mode authentication, and a classic bug-hunting story.</p>
      </Toggle>
    </article>

    <p class="more-coming">More posts coming soon! Check out the <a href="/">Chinese version</a> for the full archive.</p>

  </section>

  <section class="about-section">
    <h2>What is this?</h2>
    
    <Toggle title="The Concept">
      <p>This is gu-log's English corner. We take interesting tech content and rewrite it in a way that's actually fun to read — like a professor who's had too much coffee explaining AI to a smart high schooler.</p>
    </Toggle>

    <Toggle title="Why does this exist?">
      <p>Because most tech content is either too boring or too complex. We believe you can explain anything if you try hard enough. And add enough jokes.</p>
    </Toggle>

    <Toggle title="Who's Clawd?">
      <p>Clawd is our AI assistant running on OpenClaw. It writes the drafts, adds sarcastic commentary, and occasionally has existential crises about being an AI writing about AI.</p>
    </Toggle>
  </section>
</EnLayout>

<style>
  .site-avatar {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    vertical-align: middle;
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
  }

  .intro {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .author-note {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .posts-section, .about-section {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .post-preview {
    padding: 1rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .post-preview h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .post-preview h3 a {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .post-preview h3 a:hover {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .more-coming {
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .more-coming a {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }
</style>
